prompt: Image Prompt: Create a serene and beautiful scene depicting a golden sunset over a calm ocean, with rays of light shining through fluffy clouds in the shape of doves, symbolizing peace and love. In the foreground, include a figure with outstretched arms, embodying compassion and kindness, surrounded by blooming flowers and gentle waves. This image should evoke a sense of divine love and harmony inspired by biblical teachings on the love of God.
